{"type": "article", "id": 4294, "title": "Dachi Tea 台湾茶", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-11T07:46:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155855s9jGFOe1gI6Qad2W.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在 Kickstarter 上做智能产品众筹的创业者不在少数，但如果换成茶叶呢？日前，Kickstarter 上线了一款茶叶设计作品，是两个曾在台湾学习中文的外国人 Nicholas Palumbo 与 Simon George Thomas 做的。两人在台湾时对当地的茶叶产生了兴趣，于是跑去深山里寻找台湾茶叶。之后两人在 4 位茶叶专家的协助下，推出了自有品牌的茶叶 Dachi Tea 。这款茶叶更惊艳的部分在于其包装设计，采用了平板巧克力的包装形式，并为其设计了一个表现制茶过程循环的视觉标识。Dachi Tea 在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/highmountaintea/dachi-tea-the-high-mountain-experience\" target=\"_blank\">Kickstarter </a>上的起售价为 32 美元，如若你的赞助金额达到 5000 美元时，还可以与两位创始人一起去台湾感受一趟采茶制茶的旅程。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155852k86oqIZNU1JbBPpO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061558532QHeFI93DjtWiCLB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155853hGV3OHAurdt2PDYX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061558530Y2cSGLXWVeJd5MR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061558547EPgSvHtpiqM8nya.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155854NRg3eOWKEIPmjdk9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.8859375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}